LAGOS – 5Five 4Four Limited (54 for short) is an African-oriented Nigerian Mixed Martial Arts (MMA) professional promotion company, tailoring its productions, fights and events to not only Nigerians but viewers on the African continent. 54 announces the first-ever face-off fight night in Africa’s most-populated city, Lagos as it brings mixed martial art fighters to slug it out in a bid to leave an impeccable MMA imprint in Nigeria and by extension, the African continent. Face-Off Fight Night is a series of elite fight events organized by 54 Limited and powered by the UFC Welterweight World Champion Kamaru “The Nigerian Nightmare” Usman featuring 5MMA fighters from Nigeria and Africa, celebrities and special guests. Malcomines Win Jos International Polo Tournament 33 Teams Scramble For Glory In Jos International Polo Tourney 5 (five) professional MMA fights featuring AKO Season 1 and international fighters will compete in 1 night live at the Lagos Continental Hotel on the 7th of January, 2022. Meet the contenders for the inaugural fight night: Big Shark VS Machine Gun, Hurricane VS Resident Ninja, Marine Boxer VS Black Panther, Nicotine VS Ring Beast.